trans-unit.source: Represents a subscription to a timer event.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en prenumeration på en timerhändelse.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] TimerEventSubscription objects are added to the timer queue associated with a workflow instance in order to send a message to a specific <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> at a specified time.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]TimerEventSubscription objekt läggs till i timerkön som associeras med en arbetsflödesinstans för att skicka ett meddelande till en specifik <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>vid en viss tidpunkt.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>

trans-unit.source: When the time specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> is reached, the workflow runtime engine sends a message containing the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: När tid som anges av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>uppnås arbetsflödet runtime engine skickar ett meddelande som innehåller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A>till den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>angivna <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: The timer queue associated with a workflow instance is contained in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.
trans-unit.target: Köns timern som associeras med en arbetsflödesinstans ingår i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: You can examine <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to determine which activities are waiting on a specific TimerEventSubscription.
trans-unit.target: Du kan undersöka <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>och <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo>objekt som returnerats av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>att avgöra vilka aktiviteter som väntar på en specifik TimerEventSubscription.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> both use timer event subscriptions to provide part of their functionality.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>och <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService>timer händelseprenumerationer använder en del av deras funktioner.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>
